		<td><b>Mappers that Emulators forgot about</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />The simple question is, what is the proper mapper number for the Maxi-15 and Super Mario Bros+Tetris+Nintendo World Cup carts?  I don't know if there is any "recognized" number for these carts, but there should be.  Unlike other newer dumps, as these games use unusual mappers (the Maxi-15 mapper being documented only recently.)  I get no luck with using mapper 47 for the SMB multi or 231 for the Maxi-15 on most emulators.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

	<table width="85%" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center">
	<tr>
