	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b></b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Maxi-15 is mapper 234, not 231 (and the mapper info has been available for at least 3 years now, if not longer)
<br />
<br />SMB+Tetris+NWC, on the other hand, was never assigned a proper mapper.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

	<table width="85%" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center">
	<tr>
