	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Easy way: Make the stuff on the end a proper UNIF file but without the prg and chr chunks. Then emulators can reuse their existing UNIF loaders, and IPS patches continue to work.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


