		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="quotetitle">Great Hierophant wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">I don't know why Tetris needs an MMC1 when all it has is 32KB of PRG ROM and 16KB of CHR ROM.  A CNROM cart would do just as well.</div>
<br />MMC1, unlike CNROM, can bankswitch two independent 4 KB CHR banks. I think the ending screens for a high score in A-type and completing B-type use this.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
